Sentencas: In this work, the NiO-8YSZ/BYSZ half-cells for planar ASCs with the large size of 30 cm x 30 cm are prepared by optimizing both the sintering characteristics and the sintering temperature.
Titulo: Anode supported planar solid oxide fuel cells with the large size of 30 cm x 30 cm via tape-casting and co-sintering technique

Sentencas: The shrinkage rates, open porosities and flexural strength of the half cells are investigated systematically.
Titulo: Anode supported planar solid oxide fuel cells with the large size of 30 cm x 30 cm via tape-casting and co-sintering technique

Sentencas: The large size half-cells which are prepared by the tape-casting, co-sintering and two-step sintering method show the optimal comprehensive performances with the sintering temperature being 1350 degrees
Titulo: Anode supported planar solid oxide fuel cells with the large size of 30 cm x 30 cm via tape-casting and co-sintering technique
Anode supported planar solid oxide fuel cells with the large size of 30 cm x 30 cm via tape-casting and co-sintering technique

Sentencas: The NiO+8YSZ/8YSZ/LSM+8YSZ anode-supported single cells are obtained at the sintering temperature of 1050 degrees C.
Titulo: Anode supported planar solid oxide fuel cells with the large size of 30 cm x 30 cm via tape-casting and co-sintering technique

Sentencas: The maximum measurement power at output voltage of 0.8 V of the two cells and 1.6 V of the stack can reach 32.6 W, 34.7 W and 67.3 W, respectively.
Titulo: Anode supported planar solid oxide fuel cells with the large size of 30 cm x 30 cm via tape-casting and co-sintering technique

Sentencas: The two-cells stack is successively discharged under constant current of 5 A for 316 h with the degradation rate of 1.58% kh(-1) and 30 A for 1161 h with no degradation at the temperature of 750 degrees C.
Titulo: Anode supported planar solid oxide fuel cells with the large size of 30 cm x 30 cm via tape-casting and co-sintering technique

Sentencas: The large size ASCs show the good mechanical strength and an acceptable degradation.
Titulo: Anode supported planar solid oxide fuel cells with the large size of 30 cm x 30 cm via tape-casting and co-sintering technique
